ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿相認"},{"pid":"45bcbae46e2d10eb149c2e0704cc0941c03477cd","tid":2159852,"uid":315760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"拋m記啲茄汁醬上轉緊嘅風扇到<br />\n<br />\n結果隔離個牆好似有命案發生咁<br />\n<br />\n兩年後番個個課室啲醬仲留係度，不過淡左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8feda8745cfe891fd2c4759c1ff11e83f953f73a","tid":2159852,"uid":320110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"拉住個阿sir一齊睇gay porn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ba4ccf307674a15850730b97965f470c56270f","tid":2159852,"uid":231843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"摸miss大脾<br />\n（差啲就食到個miss)"}]}